{"tid":1589480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港旗幟「榮光獅子旗」","createTime":"2019-09-23T10:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T10:29:58.000Z","uid":265268,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec490299dcede58b9f768c3beabac8fa5b9e76c","tid":1589480,"uid":265268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:03:56.000Z","msg":"隔離有郭嘉巴 post 講香港旗，我都試吓 post 我哋嘅最新設計。<br />\n我同意 TG group 主所講，唔一定要投票選一枝出來做代表，一來唔夠時間，二來認受性不足。如果黑荊旗、龍獅旗、英美旗、Chinazi旗、連儂旗、攬炒旗、巴絲自己設計嘅旗... 全部出哂，你話幾壯觀！<br />\n至於未來真正嘅香港旗，歷史自會有定奪（好似願榮光咁）<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，以下係我哋嘅「榮光獅子旗」<br />\n我哋想將香港人一直以來守護嘅普世價值（民主、自由、法治），歷史傳承（大英、獅子山精神），加上香港特有嘅抗爭史（和理非、勇武、還眼、獅子山人鏈等），創造出類似飛獅 Winged Lion 嘅神靈來守護香港（並非鷹頭的獅鳥 Griffin）。<br />\n獅子金鬃昂首，背有自由之翼，口銜正義之劍，頸掛橄欖枝，右眼為守護香港而失去。<br />\n黑暗之時，香港流下血與淚，但獅頂上仍發出五色光芒（五大訴求），令世人注目；<br />\n光復之時，血已凝乾，在太平洋上自由飛翔。<br />\n<br />\n民族旗：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgqV7rw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgqV7rw.png&h=40cd5f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭旗：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bPgBRTc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbPgBRTc.png&h=52cf04cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iyJAokM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiyJAokM.png&h=b619b4c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n創作理念：<br />\n金色昂首獅子，代表民主、光明、大英傳承、新獅子山精神。<br />\n藍色自由之翼，代表自由、智慧、靈活如水。<br />\n白色正義女神之劍，代表法治、公義、專業界別守護。<br />\n綠色橄欖枝葉，代表和平、希望、和理非十八區發聲。<br />\n紅色勇士之血，代表勇氣、犧牲、勇武抗爭。<br />\n民族旗為白藍背景，代表光復香港，自由民族。<br />\n抗爭旗為黑色背景，代表哀悼香港。五色鐳射代表五大訴求，紅金白綠藍為撤惡法、真普選、查警暴、非暴動、銷控罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n=====<br />\n<br />\n另外我哋放咗其他設計上 Google drive （包括藍白龍獅旗）<br />\n由於並非專業設計師，請多多指教！<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/u/1/folders/1vdCno-Y-idc-LFPj6-AcdMq-VW--Sshz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Fu%2F1%2Ffolders%2F1vdCno-Y-idc-LFPj6-AcdMq-VW--Sshz&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK61cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=9915af7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/u/1/folders/1vdCno-Y-idc-LFPj6-AcdMq-VW--Sshz</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpaK0PL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpaK0PL.png&h=3af8c813&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea408b22c55954a06b4c77b229d12b10f0c19892","tid":1589480,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"[緊急][公投][置頂] 10.1集合定分區搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589182</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c11bc3914fb0fed4978554e31e020e60c5e46b80","tid":1589480,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:04:59.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[一至五帶風向]教大家phone-in節目提高駁入直播室嘅成功率<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a2b069570662f9f1b7fcd09861adc402b3107744","tid":1589480,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:05:07.000Z","msg":"圖案太大<br />\n會唔會縮細返好啲？"},{"pid":"14ced91da8b422bafe30e78a1ec9a10d1f154415","tid":1589480,"uid":166405,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:06:00.000Z","msg":"講真好核突，公仔太大，顏色太雜"},{"pid":"62cf27b5a3abb366b0671451766893cf4651cfc0","tid":1589480,"uid":265268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2b069570662f9f1b7fcd09861adc402b3107744","tid":1589480,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:05:07.000Z","msg":"圖案太大<br />\n會唔會縮細返好啲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"都有諗過, 可以試吓"},{"pid":"fbaa26f3c70b80b97929dc4ac4c94f07b6c1930d","tid":1589480,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:07:36.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌  你畫一百支旗出黎都唔夠一個義士拳頭硬啦"},{"pid":"b37c45cb61e0a817840b349bd8e738c93a722c19","tid":1589480,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dis